  "title": "Head Chef",
  "description": "<p>💓Surrey Hills Grocer is an expanding brand that aims to be the most authentic Australian destination grocer by bringing honest-to-good, fine, fresh products. Inspired by the harsh terrains of Australia, we strive to bring you the best produce and offer everyone a taste of warm Australian hospitality.💓</p><p>On top of the Australian cafe and restaurant concept, we also have <strong>Spanish, Taiwanese and Japanese restaurant concepts.</strong></p><p><strong>📢Benefits :</strong></p><ul><li>Staff meal provided 💎</li><li>Staff discount 💎</li><li>Monthly sales incentives 💎</li><li>Overtime pay 💎</li><li>Variable Bonus 💎</li><li>Medical & Dental benefits 💎</li></ul><p>As a <strong>Head Chef</strong>, you are required to:</p><p><ul><li>Oversee daily kitchen operations to ensure consistent quality and timely food service</li><li>Plan menus, develop recipes, and manage food costing in line with business targets</li><li>Lead, train, and supervise kitchen staff, including rostering and performance management</li><li>Ensure compliance with food hygiene, health, and safety regulations</li><li>Manage inventory, ordering, supplier coordination, and control food wastage</li><li>Collaborate with management to align kitchen operations with overall business goals</li><li>Maintain culinary standards, presentation, and brand consistency</li><li>Drive kitchen efficiency, innovation, and continuous improvement<br /><br /><strong>Requirement:</strong></li><li><p>Proven experience as a Head Chef or Senior Sous Chef in a similar dining environment<br /></p></li></ul></p>",
